OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 31 MAR
OL,4,CCHANNELS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1986FBBC Two's new on-screen clock
OL,7,Fairs for the first time at 1.05am, at
OL,8,Fclosedown.
OL,9,
OL,10,FAnnouncer David Wheal is on duty: "Well
OL,11,Fthere's the first look at our new clock
OL,12,Fhere on 2, which completes the brand
OL,13,Fnew image which I hope you like.
OL,14,
OL,15,F"If you do, then why not join us all
OL,16,Fagain at some point tomorrow..."
