OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 31 MAR
OL,4,CCHANNELS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG2000FUK Arena is replaced by UK
OL,7,FDrama.
OL,8,
OL,9,FUK Arena launched on 1st November 1997,
OL,10,Fspecialising in arts programming.
OL,11,
OL,12,FThe channel was part of the UKTV
OL,13,Fnetwork of channels. UKTV was a joint
OL,14,Fventure between the BBC and Flextech.
OL,15,
OL,16,FPoor ratings resulted in a shift of
OL,17,Ffocus to drama and a rebranding to UK
OL,18,FDrama.
OL,19,
OL,20,FIt would be rebranded again: first in
OL,21,FMarch 2004 to UKTV Drama and again in
OL,22,FOctober 2008, to Alibi, from which
OL,23,Sppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
